import React from 'react' const TH_Sep19 = () => { return (

Date: Thursday September, 19, 2019

Start Time: 12:35PM

Pre-Summary: The objective of this meeting should be to recap on the action items that were discussed in the last meeting on Sunday. Also we should discuss the general idea of the project like features we want to include and APIs we want to use.

Discussion Notes:

  • Features we want to include:
    • Add button
    • Remove button
    • Edit entry button
    • Review past recipets (history)
      • Dated in the Database
    • View list of inventory
      • Similar to Google Photos, ideally
  • APIs we want to use:
    • Google OCR
    • Barcode Scanner
    • Look into a food API

Sprint Goals:

Have Done By: Sunday, September 22, 2019 @ 8PM

  • Brian look into the APIs and recap us at the next meeting
  • Malik draw a general mock up

End Time: 1:45PM

) }; export default TH_Sep19
